<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Movie Date Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .poster {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff6f61;
            font-size: 3em;
        }
        p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ff3b30;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="poster">
        <h1>Hey You!</h1>
        <p>How about we make our own rom-com moment?</p>
        <p>Join me for a movie date this weekend!</p>
        <p>We can grab some ice cream, go for a ride,</p> 
           <p> and enjoy the sunset together.</p>
        <a href="#" class="button">Say Yes!</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
